org.springframework.data.keyvalue.core

接口 KeyValueAdapter

  • 所有超级接口:
    DisposableBean
    所有已知实现类:
    AbstractKeyValueAdapter, MapKeyValueAdapter

    public interface KeyValueAdapter
extends DisposableBean
    KeyValueAdapter unifies access and shields the underlying key/value specific implementation.
